{"title":"党旗颂（外一首）","authors":["刘兰松"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":6,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗颂（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘兰松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥镰割除旧中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举锤砸断铁锁链。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前赴后继八十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗卷过霞满天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰锤均是特殊材料铸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝聚多少先烈血与汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举党旗朝前迈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世纪里更灿烂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红船颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南湖红船是宝船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨如磐金光闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得黑夜忙后退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命火种遍地燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南湖红船是利剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈风斩浪排艰险。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破千重邪妖雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗染红半边天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南湖红船是神船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹雨打身不翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党是舵手指航向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披荆斩棘永向前。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}